value:
/* Please insert some values for the @@collection and @value bind parameters */
FOR tds IN thermodatasets
    FILTER tds.properties.name == "CEMDATA18"
    FOR v IN 1..1 INBOUND tds pulls
        FILTER v.properties.aggregate_state == 4
        SORT v.properties.symbol
        RETURN { symbol: v.properties.symbol, 
            G0: ROUND(v.properties.sm_gibbs_energy.values[0]), 
            H0: ROUND(v.properties.sm_enthalpy.values[0]), 
            S0: ROUND(v.properties.sm_entropy_abs.values[0]*100)/100, 
            V0: ROUND(v.properties.sm_volume.values[0]*1000)/1000, 
            Cp0: ROUND(v.properties.sm_heat_capacity_p.values[0]*10)/10, 
            HKFa1: ROUND(v.properties.eos_hkf_coeffs.values[0]*10 *10000) /10000,
            HKFa2: ROUND(v.properties.eos_hkf_coeffs.values[1]*0.01 *10000) /10000,
            HKFa3: ROUND(v.properties.eos_hkf_coeffs.values[2]*1 *10000) /10000,
            HKFa4: ROUND(v.properties.eos_hkf_coeffs.values[3]*0.0001 *10000) /10000,
            HKFc1: ROUND(v.properties.eos_hkf_coeffs.values[4]*1 *10000) /10000,
            HKFc3: ROUND(v.properties.eos_hkf_coeffs.values[5]*0.0001 *10000) /10000,
            HKFw:  ROUND(v.properties.eos_hkf_coeffs.values[6]*0.00001 *10000) /10000}
name: thermoProp_HKF_aq_cem18

FOR phs IN phases
    FILTER phs.properties.sourcetdb == {"12": "THEREDA"} && phs.properties.symbol == "aq"
    FOR mm IN 1..1 INBOUND phs mixing 
    FOR intp IN 1..1 INBOUND mm specific
    RETURN { G0 : intp.properties.intpar.values}

value:
FOR tds IN thermodatasets
    FILTER tds.properties.symbol == "PSI-Nagra-12-07"
    FOR s IN 1..1 INBOUND tds pulls
    FILTER ["AUG20_GEMS:2001:dat:         "] ANY == s.properties.comment
    FOR r IN 1..1 INBOUND s defines
    RETURN r
name: link_datasources_1
